
= ecovillage in the middle of Ireland

URL =  http://www.thevillage.ie/

=Description=

"The Cloughjordan Ecovillage brings together a diverse group of people creating an innovative new community in Tipperary. We’re doing this a way that is democratic, healthy and socially enriching while minimising ecological impacts. Our 67-acre site includes beautiful and fertile land where we grow our own food, and plants and trees to promote biodiversity."

